rComments: Fascinating guy and excellent lecturer. A true academic, Kenzie has high expectations of graduate-level students. Do the readings, go to class, and ensure your writing is at an appropriate level (no shame in taking workshops), and you'll do well.
Trying so hard to make this course interesting but ending up frustrating and confusing us. I still have no idea what this course is about or how muted this dude is when it comes to teaching.

I was so confused the entire course. There were no assignment outlines or clear instructions rather just due dates where you were confused what the assignment was. I don't understand how he even teaches. More so him just using investigation words.
